t in any of our writings. \n% REMEMBER: Continous integration may be the string that holds your current software galaxy together.\n\n> More technically, I am interested in how things bounce around in\n> computer systems. I am not sure if these two things are relted,\n> but I hope continuous integration will help me.\n> [^]{Software Curious Person expressing her hopes for Continuous Integration}\n\n","attribs":"|m+2cj+2*0+9|4+8c*0|3+53*0+26|2+2"},"pool":{"numToAttrib":{"0":["author","a.PRabeGfk5jCXUq8V"]},"nextNum":1},"head":11,"chatHead":-1,"publicStatus":false,"passwordHash":null,"savedRevisions":[]},"globalAuthor:a.PRabeGfk5jCXUq8V":{"colorId":"#0c8ae5","name":"CH","timestamp":1517858520058,"padIDs":"observatory.guide.continuousintegration"}}